high_descs: Turn around and walk to the right side of the white table with the coffee maker on it.
Pick up the spatula on the table.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Rinse off the spatula in the left sink.
Turn around and walk back to the white table, this time the front part.
Place the spatula on the table in front of the sponge.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean spatula on a table.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the small table to your left.
Grab the spatula between the lettuce and coffee maker on the table.
Turn left and walk to the sinks straight ahead.
Place the spatula in the left sink, wash it and remove it.
Turn right, walk straight, make a quick right and walk to the small table.
Stand the spatula next to the sponge on the small table.
anns.task_desc: Stand a clean spatula next to the sponge on the small table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the white table.
Pick up the wooden spoon at the edge of the table.
Turn left and walk towards the kitchen sink.
Place the wooden spoon inside the sink and turn on the faucet, then turn it off and pick up the spoon.
Turn around and walk towards the white table.
Place the wooden spoon on the table.
anns.task_desc: Wash the wooden spoon and place it back on the white table in the kitchen.
